WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.180 --> 00:00:05.900
 See how to divide a disk into partitions. 

00:00:06.540 --> 00:00:11.020
 The method works on Windows 7, 8 and 10 

00:00:12.120 --> 00:00:15.880
 In order to create a partition, we will use the tool 

00:00:16.240 --> 00:00:18.620
 embedded in Windows. 

00:00:19.480 --> 00:00:22.780
 Tools allow you to create new partitions, 

00:00:23.160 --> 00:00:26.560
 their formatting, deletion and resizing 

00:00:27.180 --> 00:00:29.820
 without losing data on existing partitions. 

